<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb573a8de-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s285g–1"><num value="285g–1">§ 285g–1.</num><heading> Sudden infant death syndrome research</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Director of the Institute shall conduct and support research which specifically relates to sudden infant death syndrome.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb573a8df-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/act/1944-07-01/ch373">July 1, 1944, ch. 373</ref>, title IV, § 449, as added <ref href="/us/pl/99/158/s2">Pub. L. 99–158, § 2</ref>, <date date="1985-11-20">Nov. 20, 1985</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/99/856">99 Stat. 856</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
